headline: Otis Declares Quarterly Dividend of $0.39 per Share
summary: The Otis Worldwide Corporation (NYSE: OTIS) Board of Directors today declared a quarterly dividend of $0.39 per share of Otis' common stock. The dividend will be payable on March 7, 2025, to shareholders of record at the close of business on February 14, 2025.
